data.description: Beautiful & cozy 2 story home, located in desirable Shiloh Crossing.  3 bedroom, 2.5 bath designed with an open concept floor plan, tile flooring & granite countertops throughout.  The large master bedroom is on the 1st floor. Home features a spacious loft and relaxing balcony. Mature landscaping with a great curb appeal Sprinkler system front & backyard. Excellent schools.  Must see!
